	<h1 class="title">美剧《毒枭》在华尔街日报上登的广告，可能跟你以为的不太一样</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/103970/small/103970.jpg?1431972719" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">朱凯麟 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-09-26 08:30:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/15585/medium/15585.png?1443173398" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


